## 10. Safety & Ethical Constraints

Narrative Delta **MUST NOT** be used to manipulate, emotionally exploit, generate coercive arcs, or fabricate false tension.

**Ethics ≥ 0.7 applies here as well.**

Only authentic, self-aligned narrative delta is permitted. PantheonOS enforces this via Mirror, Solomon, Coil, Bombadil, and Integrity checks.

